Uses of Package
org.yajasi.JungleJepps

Packages that use org.yajasi.JungleJepps
org.yajasi.JungleJepps This package contains all of the custom code to run YAJASI Jungle Jepps Desktop. 
org.yajasi.JungleJepps.db This package manages all the database connections and settings. 
org.yajasi.JungleJepps.jjtp This package contains all of the network communications for Jungle Jepps. 
org.yajasi.JungleJepps.pdf This package manages the PDF rendering and the management of the local file repository. 
org.yajasi.JungleJepps.ui This package manages the User Interface and the connection between the user and services that Jungle Jepps provides.
